- DEFI_KATOMUSD
- DEFI_KOMGUSD
- DEFI_KOXTUSD
- DEFI_KXBTEUR
- DEFI_KETHEUR

### times

The amount to multiply the result by (since Solidity does not handle decimals).

#### Solidity example

```solidity
req.addInt("times", 100);
```

# Chainlink Examples

